 each appeared in a hit comedy film in which they played most scenes dressed as a woman.  </p>
<p>

Several roles in modern plays and musicals are played by a member of the opposite sex (rather than a character cross-dressing), such as the character Edna Turnblad in <it>Hairspray</it>&nbsp;&mdash; played by <actor wordnetid="109765278" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../702/204702.xml">
