Julie Andrews</link></writer>
</actor>
</person>
 in <it><movie wordnetid="106613686" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../525/242525.xml">
Victor/Victoria</link></movie>
</it>, or a woman acting as a woman pretending to be a man, like <person wordnetid="100007846" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
